ingredientsDesc:
Elecsys CYFRA 21-1
M      Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 6.5 mL:
        Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1     Anti-cytokeratin 19-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 10 mL:
        Biotinylated monoclonal anti-cytokeratin 19 antibody (KS 19.1; mouse)
        1.5 mg/L, phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 7.2; preservative.
R2     Anti-cytokeratin 19-Ab~Ru(bpy)  10 mL:
        Monoclonal anti-cytokeratin 19 antibody (BM 19.21; mouse)
        labeled with ruthenium complex 2 mg/L; phosphate buffer
        100 mmol/L, pH 7.2; preservative.

Elecsys CYFRA 21-1 CalSet
CYFRA Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
CYFRA Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Cytokeratin (human, from cell line MCF-7) in two concentration ranges
 (approx. 0 ng/mL and approx. 50 ng/mL) in a human serum matrix.

m07.before:
體外診斷試劑；在體外以免疫分析法針對人類血清中的細胞角質素19 (cytokeratin 19)進行定量測試。Elecsys CYFRA 21-1 CalSet是使用於Elecsys 免疫分析儀上，針對Elecsys CYFRA 21-1定量分析法的校正品。
效能變更(適用機型)：本產品用於體外以免疫分析法定量檢測人類血清及血漿中細胞角質蛋白19(cytokeratin 19)，需搭配MODULAR ANALYTICS E170、cobas e 411/601/602免疫分析儀使用。
新增效能：本產品(規格：07299966190)用於體外以免疫分析法定量檢測人類血清及血漿中細胞角質蛋白19(cytokeratin 19)，需搭配cobas e 801免疫分析儀使用。
